1 - Write in a file called: "mycoolfile.txt 

the following sentence: "My very first textline in this document!".

2 - Read the document , and print the content of the file.




solution:

f = open("mycoolfile.txt", "a")
f.write("My very first textline in this document!")
f.close()

#open and read the file after the appending:
f = open("mycoolfile.txt", "r")
print(f.read())
